---
title: 数学资源 | 我的资源库
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    {% include "head.njk" %}
    <style>
        /* 数学页面专属样式 */
        .math-layout {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        /* 左侧内容区 */
        .math-content {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0; /* 防止溢出 */
        }

        /* 右侧快速导航 */
        .quick-nav {
            width: 200px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 2rem;
            align-self: start;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 1.25rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .quick-nav h4 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #1e293b;
            border-left: 3px solid #2563eb;
            padding-left: 0.75rem;
        }
        .quick-nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .quick-nav li {
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        .quick-nav a {
            display: block;
            color: #475569;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.375rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .quick-nav a:hover {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        /* 章节样式 */
        .math-section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .section-title-math {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-left: 5px solid #2563eb;
            padding-left: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .section-sub {
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* 文档卡片网格（复用原卡片样式，但在此页面单独定义） */
        .doc-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        .doc-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .doc-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 20px -8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        .doc-card-content {
            padding: 1.25rem;
        }
        .doc-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        .doc-card p {
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .doc-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .doc-btn:hover {
            background: #1d4ed8;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .math-layout {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .quick-nav {
                width: 100%;
                position: static;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }
            .quick-nav ul {
                display: flex;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 0.5rem;
            }
            .quick-nav li {
                margin-bottom: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        {% include "header.njk" %}

        <div class="math-layout">
            <!-- 右侧快速导航（放在左侧内容前，但通过flex顺序调整） -->
            <div class="quick-nav">
                <h4>📑 快速导航</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#basic">🔹 基础</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#intermediate">🔸 进阶</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#advanced">🔺 高难</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- 左侧内容区 -->
            <div class="math-content">
                <!-- 基础部分 -->
                <section id="basic" class="math-section">
                    <div class="section-title-math">📘 基础</div>
                    <div class="section-sub">代数、几何、初等函数 · 夯实根基</div>
                    <div class="doc-grid">
                        <div class="doc-card">
                            <div class="doc-card-content">
                                <h3>初等数学公式手册.pdf</h3>
                                <p>涵盖代数、三角、几何基础公式，适合快速查阅。</p>
                                <a href="/docs/elementary_math.pdf" target="_blank" class="doc-btn">在线预览</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="doc-card">
                            <div class="doc-card-content">
                                <h3>函数与图像详解.pdf</h3>
                                <p>一次函数、二次函数、指数对数函数图像性质分析。</p>
                                <a href="/docs/functions.pdf" target="_blank" class="doc-btn">在线预览</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="doc-card">
                            <div class="doc-card-content">
                                <h3>立体几何入门.pdf</h3>
                                <p>点线面位置关系、空间向量初步，配有例题。</p>
                                <a href="/docs/geometry_basic.pdf" target="_blank" class="doc-btn">在线预览</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- 进阶部分 -->
                <section id="intermediate" class="math-section">
                    <div class="section-title-math">📙 进阶</div>
                    <div class="section-sub">微积分、线性代数、概率统计 · 能力提升</div>
                    <div class="doc-grid">
                        <div class="doc-card">
                            <div class="doc-card-content">
                                <h3>微积分核心笔记.pdf</h3>
                                <p>极限、导数、积分，包含重要定理与经典例题。公式示例：{% raw %}\[ \int_{0}^{1} x^2 dx = \frac{1}{3} \]{% endraw %}</p>
                                <a href="/docs/calculus_notes.pdf" target="_blank" class="doc-btn">在线预览</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="doc-card">
                            <div class="doc-card-content">
                                <h3>线性代数精讲.pdf</h3>
                                <p>矩阵、行列式、特征值，结合几何意义讲解。</p>
                                <a href="/docs/linear_algebra.pdf" target="_blank" class="doc-btn">在线预览</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="doc-card">
                            <div class="doc-card-content">
                                <h3>概率论与数理统计.pdf</h3>
                                <p>随机变量、分布函数、参数估计，实例丰富。</p>
                                <a href="/docs/probability.pdf" target="_blank" class="doc-btn">在线预览</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- 高难部分 -->
                <section id="advanced" class="math-section">
                    <div class="section-title-math">📕 高难</div>
                    <div class="section-sub">实分析、泛函、拓扑 · 深度拓展</div>
                    <div class="doc-grid">
                        <div class="doc-card">
                            <div class="doc-card-content">
                                <h3>实分析基础.pdf</h3>
                                <p>测度论、勒贝格积分，适合高年级本科生及研究生。</p>
                                <a href="/docs/real_analysis.pdf" target="_blank" class="doc-btn">在线预览</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="doc-card">
                            <div class="doc-card-content">
                                <h3>泛函分析导论.pdf</h3>
                                <p>赋范空间、线性算子、谱理论初步。</p>
                                <a href="/docs/functional_analysis.pdf" target="_blank" class="doc-btn">在线预览</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="doc-card">
                            <div class="doc-card-content">
                                <h3>拓扑学基础.pdf</h3>
                                <p>点集拓扑、同伦论简介，抽象思维训练。</p>
                                <a href="/docs/topology.pdf" target="_blank" class="doc-btn">在线预览</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>

        {% include "footer.njk" %}
    </div>

    <script>
        // 平滑滚动（可选，配合锚点）
        document.querySelectorAll('.quick-nav a').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                const targetId = this.getAttribute('href').substring(1);
                const targetElement = document.getElementById(targetId);
                if (targetElement) {
                    targetElement.scrollIntoView({
                        behavior: 'smooth',
                        block: 'start'
                    });
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>